name: Agog 5 Cloud Scribble Iridescent
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D scribble sculpture with clashing lines. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
